	<h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>KSIR ("us") takes the privacy of users and the protection of personal information very seriously. We may collect and use information about you when you use our products and / or services. We want to explain to you through the KSIR Privacy Policy ("this Privacy Policy") how we collect, use, save, share, and transfer this information when you use our products and / or services, and the access we provide you , Update, delete, and protect this information.</p>
